                        <interp inst="t18361128-name-216" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY MILNER</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep the Sir John Falstaff, in Brydges-street, Covent-Garden. I received a dozen and a half of ginger-beer from the prisoner, and gave him a sovereign—he was to bring me the change.</p>
